---
// Option 3: Retro Terminal
// Monospace dominance, green-on-black accents, CRT effects, terminal-style prompts
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>DTP — Retro Terminal</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --terminal-bg: #0d1117;
      --terminal-green: #39d353;
      --bright-green: #7ee787;
      --dim-green: #238636;
      --border: #161b22;
      --text: #c9d1d9;
      --dim-text: #8b949e;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      background: var(--terminal-bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    /* CRT Scanline effect */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 1px,
        transparent 1px,
        transparent 2px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    
    /* Screen flicker animation */
    @keyframes flicker {
      0% { opacity: 0.97; }
      5% { opacity: 1; }
      10% { opacity: 0.98; }
      15% { opacity: 1; }
      20% { opacity: 0.96; }
      25% { opacity: 1; }
      100% { opacity: 1; }
    }
    
    .mono {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
    
    /* Header */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background: var(--terminal-bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }
    
    nav {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .logo::before {
      content: '>';
      color: var(--bright-green);
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 50% { opacity: 1; }
      51%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
    }
    
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--dim-text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--terminal-green);
    }
    
    .nav-links a::before {
      content: './';
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    
    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    }
    
    .terminal-window {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    
    .terminal-header {
      background: var(--border);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .terminal-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    
    .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
    .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
    .terminal-dot.green { background: #27c93f; }
    
    .terminal-title {
      margin-left: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--dim-text);
    }
    
    .terminal-body {
      padding: 2rem;
      min-height: 400px;
    }
    
    .terminal-line {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .prompt {
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .command {
      color: var(--bright-green);
    }
    
    .output {
      color: var(--text);
      margin-left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .output h1 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      animation: flicker 4s infinite;
    }
    
    .output p {
      color: var(--dim-text);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    
    .cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 10px;
      height: 1.2em;
      background: var(--terminal-green);
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-left: 2px;
    }
    
    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    
    .btn {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--terminal-green);
      color: var(--terminal-bg);
      border-color: var(--terminal-green);
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--bright-green);
      border-color: var(--bright-green);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      border-color: var(--dim-green);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--terminal-green);
    }
    
    /* Features Section */
    .features-section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .section-header {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .section-header h2::before {
      content: '# ';
      color: var(--dim-green);
    }
    
    .section-header p {
      color: var(--dim-text);
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }
    
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--terminal-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
      background: rgba(57, 211, 83, 0.05);
    }
    
    .feature-card.large {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
    
    .feature-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--bright-green);
    }
    
    .feature-card p {
      color: var(--dim-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    /* Process Section */
    .process-section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .process-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .process-list {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .process-item {
      display: flex;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .process-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .process-item:hover {
      background: rgba(57, 211, 83, 0.03);
    }
    
    .step-number {
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      background: var(--border);
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      min-width: 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .step-content {
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    .step-content h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--bright-green);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    
    .step-content p {
      color: var(--dim-text);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    
    /* CTA Section */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: var(--terminal-green);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .cta-section p {
      color: var(--dim-text);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .footer-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--dim-text);
    }
    
    .footer-text span {
      color: var(--terminal-green);
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      .feature-card.large {
        grid-column: span 1;
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .process-item {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .step-number {
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
      }
      .output h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">dtp --main</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/services">approach</a></li>
        <li><a href="/case-studies">cases</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq">faq</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="terminal-window">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
          <span class="terminal-title">dtp@ai-simplified ~ %</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="terminal-line">
            <span class="prompt">$</span>
            <span class="command">cat mission.txt</span>
          </div>
          <div class="output">
            <h1>AI Simplified</h1>
            <p>We cut through the hype, build AI that works, and prove value through real results — fast, focused, and tailored to you.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">./book-call.sh</a>
              <a href="/services" class="btn btn-secondary">./our-process.sh</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-line" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <span class="prompt">$</span>
            <span class="cursor"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why organisations work with us</h2>
        <p>$ grep -r "benefits" ./features/</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card large">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Reduced Risk</h3>
          </div>
          <p>We deliver in stages. You see progress early and avoid big-bang surprises. Every sprint ships working code.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Security by Design</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Data protection and access controls built in from day one. Not an afterthought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Reliable Delivery</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Clear scope, fixed steps, regular check-ins. No scope creep, no surprise invoices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Scales with You</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Start small, prove value, then roll out without rework. Architecture that grows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card large">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Works With Your Tools</h3>
          </div>
          <p>We integrate with common meeting, messaging, and project platforms. Zero friction onboarding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-header">
            <span class="feature-icon">[ ]</span>
            <h3>Flexible Engagement</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Your stack, our cloud, or hybrid. Whatever fits policy and budget.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="process-section">
      <div class="process-container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>Development Process</h2>
          <p>$ ./run-process.sh --verbose</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-list">
          <div class="process-item">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Discovery</h3>
              <p>Understand the problem, define success metrics, identify quick wins.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-item">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>PoC</h3>
              <p>Prove the concept works with real data. Validate assumptions fast.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-item">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>MVP</h3>
              <p>Build the minimum viable product. Ship early, iterate quickly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-item">
            <div class="step-number">04</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Pilot</h3>
              <p>Test with real users in production. Gather feedback, refine.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-item">
            <div class="step-number">05</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Full Launch</h3>
              <p>Scale to production. Handover documentation and training.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>$ Ready to build?</h2>
      <p>Stop planning, start shipping. Book a discovery call and let's discuss your AI project.</p>
      <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">./book-call.sh</a>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-text">© 2024 <span>Digital Technology Partner</span></div>
      <div class="footer-text">exit 0</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
